 last)'s 'justice advisory committee'," national review's "bench memos" blog, <a href="http://bench.nationalreview.com/post/?q=mjhjnmrhzddmztjmmdjhmzu3ztgzndrim2ywognknge">http://bench.nationalreview.com/post/?q=mjhjnmrhzddmztjmmdjhmzu3ztgzndrim2ywognknge</a>=, 7/17/07, accessed 7/17/07) </p><p><strong>right coast's mike rappaport: "(candidate full) just moved a bit closer to getting my support with his announcement of an advisory committee on legal matters. the group is filled with excellent people."</strong> (mike rappaport, "(candidate last)'s judges," right coast blog, <a href="http://rightcoast.typepad.com/rightcoast/2007/07/(candidate last)s-judge.html">http://rightcoast.typepad.com/rightcoast/2007/07/(candidate last)s-judge.html</a>, 7/17/07, accessed 7/17/07)</p></span>



